Fortis to Invest $1 Billion to Boost Growth, Chairman Singh Says

-- B y   M a l a v i k a   S h a r m a
-- 
2011-09-19T07:43:26Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-19/fortis-to-invest-1-billion-to-boost-growth-chairman-singh-says.html
Fortis Healthcare  India  Ltd. plans
to invest $1 billion over three years to boost growth in India
and overseas, Chairman Malvinder Singh told reporters in New
Delhi today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
